    <item>
      <title>Netflix 下滑，因终止共享用户数量引发增长疑虑</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/netflix-slips-after-stopping-subscriber-tally-report-downbeat-q2-revenue-2024-04-19/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Netflix 股价周五下跌，因该公司计划从 2025 年起停止共享用户数量，引发了增长担忧，分析师警告称，竞争对手可能会效仿这一举措，取消流媒体行业健康状况的关键指标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/netflix-slips-after-stopping-subscriber-tally-report-downbeat-q2-revenue-2024-04-19/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 09:25:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于 Netflix、芯片股拖累，纳斯达克指数落后于同业；美国运通提振道琼斯指数</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/wall-streets-fear-gauge-over-5-month-high-rate-cut-mideast-worries-2024-04-19/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纳斯达克指数和标准普尔 500 指数周五下跌，Netflix 是悲观的季度预测拖累最大的股票之一，而由于美联储很快降息的希望逐渐减弱，所有三个指数都出现了周跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/wall-streets-fear-gauge-over-5-month-high-rate-cut-mideast-worries-2024-04-19/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 08:29:15 GMT</pubDate>
